636
01:14:32.279 --> 01:14:39.279
And it concerns me that the Karanaki is endeavouring to start again with its responsibilities

637
01:14:39.279 --> 01:14:42.279
and allow iwi to rebuild.

638
01:14:42.279 --> 01:14:51.279
But are we sometimes causing a new problem within iwi?

639
01:14:51.279 --> 01:14:57.279
I'm very mindful of that, and I ask that question about this, and I accept the journey,

640
01:14:57.279 --> 01:15:03.279
