649
01:15:56.279 --> 01:16:04.279
It's so important to hear and to see and to feel the empathy, feel the emotion of

650
01:16:04.279 --> 01:16:10.279
what this is on both sides, because we have a job here that is so important.

651
01:16:10.279 --> 01:16:14.279
A treaty settlement is an important part in your history.

652
01:16:14.279 --> 01:16:20.279
It will be looked back on in this process here, but it's just a point of time.

653
01:16:20.279 --> 01:16:25.279
It's actually the future and what you're doing intergenerational for everybody else in

654
01:16:25.279 --> 01:16:29.279
