655
01:16:29.279 --> 01:16:33.279
some more open doors to be able to begin that new journey.

656
01:16:33.279 --> 01:16:42.279
And it doesn't come without its challenges and emotions at our end, because I

657
01:16:42.279 --> 01:16:50.279
think we all here reflect on our own home, Iwi and Appu, with what they've

658
01:16:50.279 --> 01:16:52.279
gone through in there.

659
01:16:52.279 --> 01:16:56.279
So it is quite an emotional journey that I say personally for us to actually go

660
01:16:56.279 --> 01:16:58.279
